    "body": "After reading further I have come to the understanding that due to #10759 gRPC_INSTALL is set to OFF when using ny dependency from git-submodules. Unfortunately this means that the installation guide is incorrect. Further it seems impossible to build & install on Windows with BoringSSL since the package variant does only search for openssl. \r\n\r\nI am aware that I can still build and create my own installation script but that's a lot of work :("
